<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/we-need-a-green-new-deal-to-defeat-fascism-and-reverse-inequality/">We Need a Green New Deal to Defeat Fascism and Reverse Inequality</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Economist Robert Pollin explains why the Green New Deal is the only viable response to global socioeconomic crises.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/jonas-elvander/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Jonas Elvander</a></span>, </dd>
