<article class="row hentry post-262614 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-interview tag-austerity tag-climate-change tag-climate-denial tag-extinction tag-green-new-deal tag-just-transition tag-noam-chomsky tag-robert-pollin section-environment-and-health primary_topic-environment series-covering-climate-now" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/aocs-green-new-deal-is-just-the-start-next-lets-make-it-global/" title="AOC&#8217;s Green New Deal Is Just the Start. Next Let&#8217;s Make It Global.">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0707-green-new-deal-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Rep. Alexandria Ocasio Cortez speaks about the Green New Deal at a town hall organized by the Sunrise Movement, May 13, 2019." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0707-green-new-deal-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0707-green-new-deal-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0707-green-new-deal-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0707-green-new-deal-1200x900.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
