<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/op-ed/' rel='category' class='op-ed'>Op-Ed</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/environment-and-health/' rel='section' class='environment-and-health' style='color: #0ba864;'>Environment &amp; Health</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/aocs-green-new-deal-is-just-the-start-next-lets-make-it-global/">AOC&#8217;s Green New Deal Is Just the Start. Next Let&#8217;s Make It Global.</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">The U.S. needs to play a chief role in spurring a global Green New Deal alongside a domestic one.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/michelle-chen/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Michelle Chen</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2019-07-07T15:19:31+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2019-07-07T15:19:31+00:00">July 7, 2019</time>
<div class="hide" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
<a href="https://truthout.org" itemprop="url">
<span itemprop="name">
Truthout
</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>
