<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/chomsky-by-focusing-on-russia-we-ignore-trumps-existential-threat-to-climate/">Chomsky: By Focusing on Russia, We Ignore Trump’s Existential Threat to Climate</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">We should be focused on dealing with the environmental crisis while we still have time to do so, says Noam Chomsky.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
